metatags.og:title: Mayfield: A Welcome Addition to Crown Heights
metatags.og:description: Having visited Mayfield only three times I can't say whether it's always as lively and friendly as I've seen it. But if my experiences have been any indication, this is a neighborhood spot that's filling a void—it's as successful a bar as a restaurant, gathering place as eatery, with a menu I'd eat from any day of the week.
metatags.author: Serious Eats
